677
00:31:39,510 --> 00:31:40,480
Anda bertemu

678
00:31:41,110 --> 00:31:42,640
Ayah ada di sini?

679
00:31:43,920 --> 00:31:44,720
Saat itu,

680
00:31:44,720 --> 00:31:46,680
